ByteSized, Readable, Receiver, Transmitter, NamedObject, StringSource, ChangedAt, Modifiable, Broadcaster, Listener, Repeater, Transceiver, NetworkResource, ResourcePathed, ReadableResource, Resource, Resourceful, UriIdentified
public class FtpResource extends BaseNetworkResource
Simple FTP downloader. Note that this is made to download a single FTP file and then close the connection. At this point full support of navigating around the FTP file system and examining files is not supported.
Author:
ericg
